    "body": "Absence of a currently working CMake build system makes it hard to write cross-platform software based on gRPC.\r\n\r\nLinux has a working makefile. Windows build is a nightmare. @plasticbox's version helped. The VSSolution unfortunately uses nuget, requiring manual restore of packages each time my project's solution is regenerated by CMake (which is frequent).\r\n\r\nAnd a lot of ignored pull requests signal it is not really worth investing time into my own modifications."
